Create a sample Victor Ruby script

Usage:
  victor init RUBY_FILE [--template TEMPLATE]
  victor init (-h|--help)

Options:
  -t, --template NAME
    Name of the Ruby template to use. Can be:
      standalone   a full standalone Ruby script
      dsl          a Victor DSL script
      cli          a Victor CLI compatible DSL script (default)

  -h --help
    Show this help

Parameters:
  RUBY_FILE
    Output Ruby file

Examples:
  victor init ghost.rb
  victor init ghost.rb --template standalone
